doc-summary"></div><div class=3D"sc-fzoXWK sc-fzoYkl ivrawJ" data-role=3D"r=
edoc-description"><p>Welcome to the <a href=3D"https://banquest.com/" targe=
t=3D"_blank">Banquest</a> gateway JSON API.</p>
<p>You can use our API endpoints to easily and securely charge and credit t=
ransactions.</p>
<p>To use the Banquest API, you must have a merchant account and source key=
 from the Banquest gateway.</p>
<p>To create a source key in the gateway, navigate to Control Panel &gt; So=
urce Management &gt; Create Key.</p>
<h3 id=3D"api-base-uris">API Base URIs:</h3>
<ul>
<li><p>Production API base URI:</p>
<p><code>https://api.banquestgateway.com/api/v2/</code></p>
</li>
<li><p>Sandbox API base URI:</p>
<p><code>https://api.sandbox.banquestgateway.com/api/v2/</code></p>
</li>
</ul>
<p>Please use the <code>User-Agent</code> header to identify your software,=
 so requests coming from your integration can be traced.</p>
</div></div></div></div><div id=3D"tag/processing-charges" data-section-id=
