<p>To qualify for Level 3 VISA Transactions:</p>
<p>A - The total transaction amount must be equal to the sum total of all i=
tems (unit cost =C3=97 quantity =E2=80=93 discount + tax).</p>
<p>B - The tax amount of the transaction must be equal to the sum total of =
all item tax amounts.</p>
<p>The following fields are required for Level 3 data:</p>
<ul>
<li><code>sku</code>,</li>
<li><code>description</code>,</li>
